	{
		"id": "pair_nyx_liora_bandage_and_blade",
		"unit_a": "Nyx",
		"unit_b": "Liora",
		"title": "Bandage and Blade",
		"text": "Nyx is trying to rewrap a cut on their forearm with one hand when Liora quietly takes the bandage away.\n\n\"I had it,\" Nyx mutters.\n\"You had blood on your cuff and stubbornness in your jaw,\" Liora replies. \"Those are not the same thing.\"\nNyx watches her work. \"You always sound like mercy is an order someone forgot to issue.\"\nLiora ties the knot carefully. \"And you always sound like pain is a tax you’ve already budgeted for.\"\nNyx’s expression flickers into something small and unguarded. \"Occupational hazard.\"\nLiora meets their eyes. \"Then let it be a shared one, for five minutes.\"",
